<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.6.10">
<l>aṭaintiṭ ṭamararka ḷāḻkaṭal taṉṉai</l>
<l>miṭaintiṭṭu mantaram mattāka nāṭṭi</l>
<l>vaṭamcuṟṟi vācuki vaṉkayi ṟākak</l>
<l>kaṭaintiṭṭa kaikaḷāl cappāṇi kārmukil vaṇṇaṉē cappāṇi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With the hands that,</l>
<l rend="indent">the immortals having gathered, crowding the deep sea,</l>
<l>fixed Mount Mandara as a churning rod, tied a rope around [it],</l>
<l>and churned [the sea] with Vasukī as a strong rope,</l>
<l> [clap] cappāṇi! You with the complexion of a dark cloud, [clap] cappāṇi</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
